https://github.com/hemanth-nag/Camera_Flask_App


## Build

```bash
cd ../app
#docker build . -t dcauldwell/ng-innovate-app:0.0
export CR_PAT=<personal access token>
echo $CR_PAT | docker login ghcr.io -u darrylcauldwell --password-stdin        
docker login ghcr.io -u darrylcauldwell --password-stdin
docker buildx build --platform linux/amd64,linux/arm64 . --tag ghcr.io/darrylcauldwell/ng-innovate-cv-app:latest --push
docker pull ghcr.io/darrylcauldwell/ng-innovate-cv-app:latest
docker run --network ng-innovate-net --name ng-innovate-cv-app -d -p 4000:5000 ghcr.io/darrylcauldwell/ng-innovate-cv-app:latest
```